                     Control.Concurrent.SCC.Configurable,
                     Control.Concurrent.SCC.Parallel, Control.Concurrent.SCC.Sequential
  Other-Modules:     Control.Concurrent.Configuration, Control.Concurrent.SCC.Coercions,
