                     Control.Concurrent.SCC.Combinators, Control.Concurrent.SCC.Primitives, Control.Concurrent.SCC.XML
  Build-Depends:     base < 5, containers,
                     transformers >= 0.2 && < 0.7, transformers-compat >= 0.3 && < 0.8, bytestring < 1.0, text < 3,
